                    <tr>
                        <td><sup xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">#</sup></td>
                        <td class="align_justified"><ref xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" href="hk/1997/107">107 of 1997</ref> amended <ref xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" href="/hk/cap383">Cap. 383</ref> by adding section 3(3) and (4). That section was
                            repealed by section 2 of the Hong Kong Bill of Rights (Amendment)
                            Ordinance 1998 (<ref xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" href="hk/1998/2">2 of 1998</ref>) on 28 February 1998.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><inline xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" class="force_orig_font">*</inline></td>
