                            1998 by <ref xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" href="hk/1998/ln48">L.N. 48 of 1998</ref>.</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </content>
    </editorialNote><section id="ID_1438403394024_001" name="s3" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2020-04-23" status="operational" temporalId="s3"><num value="3">3.</num><heading>Suspension of operation of Trade Unions (Amendment) (No. 2) Ordinance
            1997</heading><subsection id="ID_1438413120262_004" name="1" temporalId="s3_1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content>On and from the
                commencement*
                of this Ordinance, the Trade Unions Ordinance (<ref href="/hk/cap332">Cap.
                332</ref>) shall be read as if the amendments effected by the Trade Unions
                (Amendment)
                (No. 2)
                Ordinance 1997 (<ref href="/hk/1997/102">102 of 1997</ref>) had not been
                enacted.</content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438413120278_005" name="2" temporalId="s3_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content>Subsection (1) shall cease to have effect on 31 October
                    1997<sup>#</sup>
                or such earlier date as the Secretary for Education and Manpower appoints by notice
                in the Gazette and he may appoint different dates for the cessation of the effect of
                subsection (1) with respect to different provisions of the Trade Unions Ordinance
                    (<ref href="/hk/cap332">Cap. 332</ref>).</content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438413120278_013" name="3" temporalId="s3_3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content>The Provisional Legislative Council may by resolution made from time to time
                extend the period during which
                subsection (1)
                has effect.</content></subsection></section><editorialNote type="footnote" id="ID_1585120800391_001" class="font_size_9">
        <content>Editorial Note:</content>
        <content class="font_size_9">
