                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><sup xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">#</sup></td>
                        <td class="align_justified">On 31 October 1997, s. 4(1) and (2), to the
                            extent that it was in effect immediately before 31 October 1997, ceased
                            to have effect. Please see s. 14(2) of <ref xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" href="/hk/1997/135">135 of 1997</ref>.</td>
                    </tr>
